'''''Nous aurons toute la mort pour dormir''''' , ni 1977 filime ya documentaire ya [[Ubufaransa|Franco]] - [[Moritaniya|Mauritanian]] iyobowe na Med Hondo kandi ikorerwa muri Les Films du Soleil Ô<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0125958/</ref>.  

Iyi filime yafashwe amezi 4 kuva ku ya 25 Ukuboza 1975 kugeza ku ya 5 Werurwe 1976, mu gace kahoze ari Sahara ya [[Esipanye]]<ref>http://www.film-documentaire.fr/4DACTION/w_fiche_film/23706_1</ref>.  Iyi filime ivuga ku ntambara yitwaje intwaro ya Polisario Front mu burengerazuba bwa Sahara kurwanya ubukoloni bwa Espagne<ref>https://en.unifrance.org/movie/2935/nous-aurons-toute-la-mort-pour-dormir</ref>.  Iyi filime yakiriwe neza n'abayinenga kandi yerekanwe mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Berlin mu [[Budage]] bw'Iburengerazuba muri Kamena 1977<ref>https://www.senscritique.com/film/Nous_aurons_toute_la_mort_pour_dormir/33061358</ref>.  

